To upgrade from forum2 to forum:
- apply forum.mysql
- update node set type = "forum" where type = "forum2";
- insert into forum select * from forum2;
- drop table forum2;
- upload forum.module overwriting existing module
- in admin/site config/module, enable forum and disable forum2
- delete forum2

thanks for using this module :)

(to upgrade from the old forum module to forum(2), ask Kjartan)
